<div class="title">Does Not Resemble Amphetamine</div>
<div class="substance">Adrafinil (Olmifon)</div>
<div class="author">by <A HREF="exp.cgi?A=ShowAuthor&ID=90">Rev. MeO</A></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Rev. MeO. "Does Not Resemble Amphetamine: An Experience with Adrafinil (Olmifon) (exp10353)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Nov 2, 2001. erowid.org/exp/10353</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
